title: SMW Central - Super Mario World Hacks 2015
description:
*ALL Super Mario World hacks from smwcentral!
All Hacks are sorted by creator and difficulty.

If u love Mario and u played super mario world, than this is a must have!!
All Hacks are already patched so u are good to go. 
Just start you're Snes Emulator and you can start playing. Jou dont have a snes emulator yet than my advice is to download Zsnes 1.42 ore 1.51

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
*
- All Hacks have 22 exits or more.
- The difficulty of the hacks is determined by the creators. 
- All Hacks uploaded on smw central before 24-06-2015 (DD-MM-YYYY) are in this package.
- All the Hacks are FULL VERSION (Demo's and hacks with less than 22 exits are excluded from this package).


- Hacks with alternative characters beside Mario, Luigi, Toad and Yoshi are excluded from this package.
- Hacks that are not supported by Zsnes 1.42 are excluded from this package except by the hack ''An SMW Central Production''.


By Robert Konings
